.TH "FIXTURE" "1" "2026-06-04" "cargo-orthohelp 0.8.0" "Fixture Manual"
.SH NAME
fixture \- Nested fixture command tree.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B fixture
\fB\-\-global\fR \fIGLOBAL\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
Nested fixture command tree.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-global\fR \fIGLOBAL\fR
Global configuration value.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
\fBNESTED_APP_GLOBAL\fR
Global configuration value. Equivalent to \fB\--global\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
\fB0\fR
Successful execution.
.TP
\fB1\fR
General errors.
.SH COMMANDS
.SS greet
Greets a named recipient.
.PP
OPTIONS:
.TP
\fB\-\-excited\fR
Adds an exclamation mark to the greeting.
.TP
\fB\-\-recipient\fR \fIRECIPIENT\fR
Recipient to greet.
.SS version
Prints version information.
.SS admin
Administers fixture state.
.PP
OPTIONS:
.TP
\fB\-\-scope\fR \fISCOPE\fR
Scope to administer.
